name: AgriGuardDispute

methods.name: create_application
methods.desc: Initialize the dispute contract with enhanced features

methods.name: set_insurance_contract
methods.desc: Set the main insurance contract address (admin only)

methods.name: register_juror
methods.desc: Enhanced juror registration with staking requirement

methods.name: create_dispute
methods.desc: Enhanced dispute creation with advanced juror selection and timing

methods.name: vote_on_dispute
methods.desc: Enhanced voting system with time validation and reputation tracking

methods.name: get_total_jurors
methods.desc: Get total number of registered jurors

methods.name: get_event
methods.desc: Get a specific event by ID

methods.name: get_recent_events
methods.desc: Get recent events (returns count and starting event ID)

methods.name: get_dispute_status
methods.desc: Get enhanced dispute status with time-based information

methods.name: get_active_disputes
methods.desc: Get count of active disputes and total disputes

methods.name: validate_juror_eligibility
methods.desc: Validate juror eligibility and return status code

methods.name: get_juror_assigned_disputes
methods.desc: Get all disputes assigned to a specific juror

methods.name: is_juror_assigned_to_dispute
methods.desc: Check if a juror is assigned to vote on a specific dispute

methods.name: mark_dispute_processed
methods.desc: Mark a dispute as processed/deleted (admin only)

methods.name: trigger_policy_processing
methods.desc: Trigger policy processing in the insurance contract via inner transaction

desc:
Enhanced Dispute Resolution Contract for AgriGuard Insurance with Algorand Features

    Features:
    - Community-based dispute resolution with enhanced juror management
    - Time-based voting deadlines and dispute lifecycle management
    - Event logging and statistics tracking
    - Cross-contract communication with insurance contract
    - Asset-based juror staking system
    - Advanced voting mechanisms with reputation-based selection
